# ─── Backend API URL ──────────────────────────────────
# ⚠️ REQUIRED IN PRODUCTION (Railway).
# Set this to your backend service's full URL, e.g.:
#   VITE_API_URL=https://onestopshop-backend.up.railway.app
#
# In local dev, use the relative path (Vite dev proxy handles it):
#   VITE_API_URL=/api
VITE_API_URL=/api
